title: Was 85 children under the age of 1 infected with Coved 19 in Nefried County, Texas?
subtitle: "These children haven't even got their first birthday yet," said the Director of Public Health of the province of Añas Annette Rodríguez.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: On 17 July 2020, Nois County, Texas, underwent 85 positive COVID-19 tests among children under one year of age.
